 but I - if I went it were always under protest.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Did you ever go out with just your father, he used to take you out on train rides?
