o play myself and then of course - you grew away from your parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 But when you were small you used to go out with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 But small - yes, he used to take us out to - I can remember he used to take us up onto the moor and - run about on the moor 
and - you know, kick - kick the ball about, go for walks, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 You said he took you to Liverpool as well to see the boats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Well he - he used to - once or twice, just for a day out, probably }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235681\charrsid12214547 when}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547  he was having a - his holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Would it be just him or was your mother with you as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Oh no, me mother didn't go, not on those jaunts, no, it was too much for her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, on Bank Holidays, at E}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
