\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3039684\charrsid12214547 singing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 . Then they used to carry pots and when they got into a field there used to be games. Now }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
