 used to run it from one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3039684\charrsid12214547  p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 art, Haggas's used to run it from St John}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2235681\charrsid12214547 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 s and they used to provide these like teacakes and one thing and another. It were a case o
f the rich feeding the poor when you went down to it, these are things that you could resent today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 The milk owners sort of gave the money to provide the meal at the field?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Yes. Aye, that's right. In other words it - it was a - there was - the u
pper start and the lower strata which as we got older we realized what is was done for, how it was done and today - when you think about it - we first I laugh about it. They were really enjoyable day out because it were once a year. And - and we had fun w
ithout any doubt but - there was that today that would cause that bit of resentment between the difference of the - it does to me anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 That was a Sunday school outing, you wouldn't go with your parents to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Well they used to go you know like up in - but it was more or less - mostly to - to make sure that we - we all behaved ourselves. Oh yes.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 You don't remember going off for the day with the at the Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 No, I - I can't say that we went anywhere particularly, that was one of the day's outings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Your father would be working perhaps at Bank Holidays?
