Oh, at holiday times, I mean, they were working you see because the people that had money, if anybody had money well of course - they - the trains were running, extra trains and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Did you ever go away for a holiday, with your father's passes you'd go and stay both with his relatives and your mother's relatives?

