And then - and to Suffolk. And even today, only a few weeks ago, there was two people came from Bury St Edmunds, to see me. And I'm going to see them - and one of them - their mother's alive, she must be going up to ninety. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 She's an aunt of yours is she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5601259 CT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 Well - the - the - there's some - like relative far removed on me mother's side. But - we - I always call her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3039684\charrsid12214547 Nan}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 , but she must be going up to ninety.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11799755 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5005651\charrsid12214547 When you were on these holidays with your relatives in Derbyshire and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3039684\charrsid12214547 
